{"tid":2229712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】林泳淘新相勁似巴士司機　竟然仲同倪晨曦「撞樣」？","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T18:05:34.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d74e6ae3e42a759301fc3ade5033a7041b1f37dc","tid":2229712,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"藝人林泳淘今天（4日）在IG發布新相，表示是運動日：「其實係俾人一早摷起身捉咗去球場執波。」這張照片一出後，便被網民嘲笑她的造型很像巴士司機制服，大家都說如果不拿起籃球還以為泳淘轉行去駕駛巴士。<br />\n<br />\n另外一個點焦點是泳淘這張照片的樣貌，由於可能角度是「低炒」關係，再加上臉部有些陰影，所以差一些認不出是泳淘本人，反而感覺像倪晨曦，記者特意將二人的照片拼在一起，確實是有3分似的。。"},{"pid":"f6894bb9c9cb634d2288670c372cfbd5b9c42bf5","tid":2229712,"uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201004/389411200640880640.jpeg/LmbLHV5FnU2kXkHXUMmFi5UjFAOJMl2f9gMB1fYDAdU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201004%2F389411200640880640.jpeg%2FLmbLHV5FnU2kXkHXUMmFi5UjFAOJMl2f9gMB1fYDAdU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4ac767a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201004/389412889766793216.jpeg/OsNlj1z9U0r7-4dbI2y_KY30q2jKNstUWdIhM1nSITM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201004%2F389412889766793216.jpeg%2FOsNlj1z9U0r7-4dbI2y_KY30q2jKNstUWdIhM1nSITM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ba6bd472&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2be4ed290f9000d8e019d5c97a1dbd7fc38d7c67","tid":2229712,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200712/359013276446756864.jpeg/6XCEOsvKZEJ3HCxlPNDJOfpZMp7GmuvWDKXzEAyl8xA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200712%2F359013276446756864.jpeg%2F6XCEOsvKZEJ3HCxlPNDJOfpZMp7GmuvWDKXzEAyl8xA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4be30eec&s={